- All user inputs must be properly sanitized
- External links must use rel="noopener noreferrer"
- All code examples must follow security best practices
- No sensitive information should be hardcoded in examples
- All file operations must be safe and validated
- All dependencies must be kept up to date
- All agent actions must only run in the workspace directory with approval 
- Any action outside he workspace directory must be approved